          <path
            d="M11 12C12.1046 12 13 11.1046 13 10C13 8.89543 12.1046 8 11 8C10.6357 8 10.2942 8.09739 10 8.26756C9.4022 8.61337 9 9.25972 9 10C9 10.7403 9.4022 11.3866 10 11.7324C10.2942 11.9026 10.6357 12 11 12Z"
